title: Sanders to 'SNL': 'I have an ample supply of underwear'
text:
Published By: Iowa City Press - Today 
U.S. Sen. Bernie Sanders says he has an “ample supply of underwear,” despite how he was portrayed on "Saturday Night Live" this week.
